object.script: -- credit to PirateJake2000, used the equation used in -- their complete clutch controller -- https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2499375130

turning_divisor = property.getNumber("Turning Divisor")
function abs(x) return math.abs(x) end
function onTick() leftClutch = 0 rightClutch = 0 leftReverse = false rightReverse = false ws = math.floor(input.getNumber(1)*100)/100 ad = math.floor(input.getNumber(2)*100)/100 if ad > 0 then -- turning right leftClutch = -ad/turning_divisor rightClutch = ad/turning_divisor elseif ad < 0 then -- turning left leftClutch = -ad/turning_divisor rightClutch = ad/turning_divisor end if input.getBool(1) then rightReverse = not rightReverse leftReverse = not leftReverse end if ws > 0 then leftClutch = -leftClutch rightClutch = -rightClutch end leftClutch = ws + leftClutch rightClutch = ws + rightClutch if leftClutch < 0 then leftReverse = not leftReverse end if rightClutch < 0 then rightReverse = not rightReverse end output.setBool(1, leftReverse) output.setBool(2, rightReverse) output.setNumber(1, abs(leftClutch)) output.setNumber(2, abs(rightClutch)) output.setNumber(3, abs(ws) + abs(ad)) end

https://code.visualstudio.com/download (search "Stormworks Lua with LifeboatAPI" extension) -- By Nameous Changey -- Minimized Size: 2628 (2942) chars bA="\nyaw from tar: " bz="%.3f" by="\npitch from tar: " bx=true bw=false bv=property bu=input bt=math bs=output br=screen.drawText bq=bs.setNumber bp=bs.setBool bo=bt.abs bn=bu.getNumber bm=bt.atan bl=bv.getNumber bk=bv.getBool b=bw c=0 d=0 e=0 f=0 g=bk("Enable Debug")h=bk("Invert Horizontal Rotation")i=bk("Invert Vertical Rotation")j=bk("Aim Mode")k=bk("Requires Is Occupied?")l=bl("Horizontal Pivot Type")m=bl("Vertical Pivot Type")n=bl("Angle Units")o=bl("Horizontal Max Angle")p=bl("Horizontal Min Angle")q=bl("Vertical Max Angle")r=bl("Vertical Min Angle")s=bl("Time Between Shots (s)")t=bl("Min Mass")u=bl("Max Mass")v=bl("Min Y")w=bl("Max Y")x=bl("Yaw Threshold")y=bl("Pitch Threshold")z=bl("Min Distance")A=bl("Max Distance")B=bt.pi*2 C=4 D=4 E=1 F=1 function G(H,I,J,K)return bm(H-J,I-K)/B end function L(J,K,H,I)return bt.sqrt((H-J)^2+(I-K)^2)end function M()N=1 if n==1 then N=B elseif n==2 then N=400 elseif n==3 then N=360 end if l>=2 then C=1 end if m>=2 then D=1 end E=C if h then E=-C end F=D if i then F=-D end o=O(o/N/C)p=O(p/N/C)q=O(q/N/D)r=O(r/N/D)x=O(x/N)y=O(y/N)end function onTick()local P=bw if not b then M()b=bx end c=c+1 e=0 f=0 Q=bw R=bw S=bu.getBool(1)if not k or k and S then T=bn(10)if u==0 and t==0 or u==0 and t>=0 and T>=t or T>=t and T<=u then U=bn(2)if U>=v and U<=w then V=bn(7)W=bn(9)X=bn(1)Y=bn(3)Z=L(V,W,X,Y)if Z>=z and Z<=A+300 then bb=bn(8)bc=-bn(4)bd=bn(5)be=bn(6)bf=bn(11)*4 bg=bc-G(X,Y,V,W)e=O(bt.bh(bg,p,o)*E)if l<=1 then e=O(bi(e,-1,1))end if l>=2 then e=O(((e-bd*C)%1+1.5)%1-.5)end f=O(bt.bh(bm((U-bb)/Z)/B,r,q)*F)+bf if m>=2 then f=O(((f-be*D)%1+1.5)%1-.5)end Q=(l<=1 and bo(bd*C-e)<=x or l>=2 and bo(e)<=x)R=(m<=1 and bo(be*F-f)<=y or m>=2 and bo(f)<=y)if Q then if R then if d==0 or c-d>=s*60 then if Z<A then bp(1,bx)P=bx end end end end end end end end if not P then bp(1,bw)end bq(1,e)bq(2,f)end function onDraw()if g then if bd then if Q then br(0,0,"VALID yaw thrsh: "..(bz):format(x)..bA..(bz):format(l<=1 and bo(bd*C-e)or l>=2 and bo(e)))else br(0,0,"INVALID yaw thrsh: "..(bz):format(x)..bA..(bz):format(l<=1 and bo(bd*C-e)or l>=2 and bo(e)))end else br(0,0,"horizontal_rot doesnt exist")end if be then if R then br(0,20,"VALID pitch thrsh: "..(bz):format(y)..by..(bz):format(m<=1 and bo(be*F-f)or m>=2 and bo(f)))else br(0,20,"INVALID pitch thrsh: "..(bz):format(y)..by..(bz):format(m<=1 and bo(be*F-f)or m>=2 and bo(f)))end else br(0,20,"vertical_rot doesnt exist")end end end function bt.bh(bj,min,max)return max<bj and max or min>bj and min or bj end function O(bj)return bj~=bj and 0 or bj end function bi(bj,min,max)return(bj-min)/(max-min)%1*(max-min)+min end
